VERCEL.name: Vercel
VERCEL.tagline: Enabling developers to build and deploy web experiences with instant global edge deployment and Next.js
VERCEL.overview: Vercel is a frontend cloud platform and the creator of Next.js, the most popular React framework. Founded in 2015 by Guillermo Rauch, the company provides instant deployment, edge functions, and AI-powered development tools. In September 2025, Vercel closed a $300M Series F at $9.3B valuation—nearly 3x the $3.25B from May 2024. Vercel reached $200M ARR by May 2025, with v0 (AI coding assistant) generating $42M ARR. Next.js was downloaded more in 12 months than from 2016-2024 combined. The company launched AI Cloud in July 2025 for AI workloads.
